trans-unit.source: Instances of this class are passed to the <xref:System.Net.UploadFileCompletedEventHandler>.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別的執行個體傳遞至<xref:System.Net.UploadFileCompletedEventHandler>。</xref:System.Net.UploadFileCompletedEventHandler>

trans-unit.source: Gets the server reply to a data upload operation that is started by calling an <xref:System.Net.WebClient.UploadFileAsync*> method.
trans-unit.target: 取得伺服器回覆的資料上傳作業啟動時，藉由呼叫<xref:System.Net.WebClient.UploadFileAsync*>方法。</xref:System.Net.WebClient.UploadFileAsync*>

trans-unit.source: You should check the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> properties to determine whether the upload completed.
trans-unit.target: 您應該檢查<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>和<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A>屬性，來判斷是否已完成上傳。</xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property's value is an <xref:System.Exception> object or the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> property's value is `true`, the asynchronous operation did not complete correctly and the Result property's value will not be valid.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>屬性的值是<xref:System.Exception>物件或<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A>屬性的值是`true`、 未正確完成非同步作業和結果屬性的值將變成無效。</xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> </xref:System.Exception> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Byte> array that contains the server reply.
